---
layout: base.njk
title: Управление на имоти — TES Borovets
---
{% set lang = lang or "bg" %}
{% set t = i18n[lang] %}
{% set prefix = "" if lang == "bg" else "/en" %}

<!-- Breadcrumb -->
<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb">
  <div class="container">
    <ol class="breadcrumb-list">
      <li><a href="{{ prefix }}/">{{ t.breadcrumb_home }}</a></li>
      <li>
        <span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="bc-current">{{ t.nav_property_management }}</span>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="service-hero">
  {% set pmHeroUrl %}{% imgabs "borovets/e50ab250f2c0ad788054238682d9aa93dc8ab9d3.jpeg", "banner" %}{% endset %}
  <img src="{{ pmHeroUrl }}" alt="" class="service-hero-img" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async">
  <div class="service-hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="container service-hero-content">
    <span class="kicker" style="color: var(--color-accent-200);">TES Borovets</span>
    {% if lang == "bg" %}
      <h1>Управление на имоти</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">Пълна услуга за управление на вашия ваканционен или инвестиционен имот в Боровец</p>
    {% else %}
      <h1>Property Management</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">Full-service management for your holiday or investment property in Borovets</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Intro + Sidebar -->
<section style="padding-bottom: 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pm-content-grid">

      <div class="pm-body">
        {% if lang == "bg" %}
          <p class="lead">"ТУР ЕКСПРЕС СЕРВИС" ООД предоставя на всички свои клиенти пълна услуга за управление на имоти.</p>
          <p>Тези услуги са създадени за да задоволят напълно нуждите на всички собственици на ваканционни и инвестиционни имоти в България.</p>
        {% else %}
          <p class="lead">"TUR EXPRESS SERVICE" Ltd. provides all its clients with a comprehensive Property Management service.</p>
          <p>These services are designed to fully meet the needs of all owners of holiday and investment properties in Bulgaria.</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <aside class="pm-sidebar">
        {% if lang == "bg" %}
          <div class="pm-key-service">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined pm-key-icon" aria-hidden="true">campaign</span>
            <h4>Маркетинг</h4>
            <p>Включване в рекламни кампании, интернет, печатни издания и партньорства с туроператори.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pm-key-service">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined pm-key-icon" aria-hidden="true">chair</span>
            <h4>Обзавеждане</h4>
            <p>Три пакета модулно обзавеждане — Стандарт, Премиум и Делукс — по избор на клиента.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pm-key-service">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined pm-key-icon" aria-hidden="true">gavel</span>
            <h4>Юридически</h4>
            <p>Представителство пред власти, категоризация, договори с наематели и туроператори.</p>
          </div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="pm-key-service">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined pm-key-icon" aria-hidden="true">campaign</span>
            <h4>Marketing</h4>
            <p>Inclusion in advertising campaigns, internet, print publications and tour operator partnerships.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pm-key-service">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined pm-key-icon" aria-hidden="true">chair</span>
            <h4>Furnishing</h4>
            <p>Three modular furniture packages — Standard, Premium and Deluxe — client's choice.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pm-key-service">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined pm-key-icon" aria-hidden="true">gavel</span>
            <h4>Legal</h4>
            <p>Representation before authorities, property categorisation, contracts with tenants and tour operators.</p>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </aside>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Services checklist -->
<section class="section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    {% if lang == "bg" %}
      <span class="kicker">Пълен обхват</span>
      <h2>Какво включва управлението</h2>
      <div class="pm-checklist-grid">
        {% set items_bg = [
          "Продажба на имоти",
          "Консултантски услуги",
          "Бизнес планове и стратегии",
          "Маркетингови проучвания",
          "Представителство пред държавни и общински служби",
          "Категоризация съгласно Закона за туризма",
          "Управление на договори за наем",
          "Маркетинг за максимална възвръщаемост",
          "Рекламна стратегия — печат, радио, интернет",
          "Летни и зимни програми + пакетни цени",
          "Модулно обзавеждане по три пакета"
        ] %}
        {% for item in items_bg %}
          <div class="pm-checklist-item">
            <span class="pm-checklist-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="2 8 6 12 14 4"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="pm-checklist-text">{{ item }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <p style="max-width:72ch;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:1.7;color:var(--on-surface-variant);">Ние прилагаме нашите умения и опит в разрешаването на проблеми, типично възникващи при отдаването под наем на имоти за да осигурим както на собственика така и на наемателя пълно удовлетворение. Правейки наемателите щастливи е ключът за максимизиране на възвръщаемостта от инвестицията на клиентите ни.</p>
    {% else %}
      <span class="kicker">Full scope</span>
      <h2>What management includes</h2>
      <div class="pm-checklist-grid">
        {% set items_en = [
          "Property sales",
          "Consultancy services",
          "Business plans and strategies",
          "Market research",
          "Representation before state and municipal authorities",
          "Property categorisation under the Tourism Act",
          "Rental agreement management",
          "Marketing for maximum return on investment",
          "Advertising strategy — print, radio, internet",
          "Summer and winter programmes + package prices",
          "Modular furnishing in three packages"
        ] %}
        {% for item in items_en %}
          <div class="pm-checklist-item">
            <span class="pm-checklist-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="2 8 6 12 14 4"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="pm-checklist-text">{{ item }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <p style="max-width:72ch;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:1.7;color:var(--on-surface-variant);">We apply our skills and experience in resolving problems typically arising in property rental to ensure complete satisfaction for both the owner and the tenant. Making tenants happy is the key to maximising our clients' return on investment.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Furnishing packages -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    {% if lang == "bg" %}
      <span class="kicker">Обзавеждане</span>
      <h2>Три пакета по ваш избор</h2>
      <div class="pm-furnishing-grid">
        <div class="pm-furnishing-card">
          <span class="kicker">Пакет 01</span>
          <div class="pm-furnishing-name">Стандарт</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pm-furnishing-card">
          <span class="kicker">Пакет 02</span>
          <div class="pm-furnishing-name">Премиум</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pm-furnishing-card">
          <span class="kicker">Пакет 03</span>
          <div class="pm-furnishing-name">Делукс</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="pm-furnishing-note">Привилегията за клиентите е, че при веднъж избран пакет се дава възможност сами да определят оборудването и уредите в съответствие с интериора.</p>
    {% else %}
      <span class="kicker">Furnishing</span>
      <h2>Three packages, your choice</h2>
      <div class="pm-furnishing-grid">
        <div class="pm-furnishing-card">
          <span class="kicker">Package 01</span>
          <div class="pm-furnishing-name">Standard</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pm-furnishing-card">
          <span class="kicker">Package 02</span>
          <div class="pm-furnishing-name">Premium</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pm-furnishing-card">
          <span class="kicker">Package 03</span>
          <div class="pm-furnishing-name">Deluxe</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="pm-furnishing-note">The privilege for clients is that once a package is selected, they are able to determine the equipment and appliances themselves in accordance with the interior.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA — dark navy -->
<section class="pm-cta-section">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;padding-top:var(--space-16);padding-bottom:var(--space-16);">
    {% if lang == "bg" %}
      <h2>Имате имот в Боровец?</h2>
      <p class="pm-cta-lead">Свържете се за консултация и оценка</p>
    {% else %}
      <h2>Have a property in Borovets?</h2>
      <p class="pm-cta-lead">Get in touch for a consultation and valuation</p>
    {% endif %}
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:var(--space-4);justify-content:center;margin-top:var(--space-8);">
      <a href="{{ prefix }}/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">
        {{ "ИЗПРАТИ ЗАПИТВАНЕ" if lang == "bg" else "SEND ENQUIRY" }}
      </a>
      <a href="tel:+359888909237" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-2);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:var(--text-sm);text-decoration:none;padding:var(--space-3) var(--space-5);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);">
        {{ client.contact_phone_en }}
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
